        "Post-Baccalaureate Certificate in Music Therapy": [
            "Post-Baccalaureate Certificate in Music Therapy Rowan University’s Music Therapy Post-Baccalaureate Certificate is intended for students who have already completed a Bachelor’s in Music. This program will be offered in conjunction with the Bachelor of Music, Concentration in Music Therapy. Students in the program will be prepared to become a Board-Certified Music Therapist and to continue in graduate studies in Music Therapy."
        ],
